OL,3,CWinter fuel payments: What is changing
OL,4,Cand who will be affected?
OL,6,FWho will be affected by the cut to the
OL,7,Fwinter fuel payment? ITV News explains
OL,9,FKeir Starmer is under pressure over
OL,10,Fthe government's decision to cut the
OL,11,Fwinter fuel payment for ten million
OL,12,Fpensioners in England and Wales.
OL,14,FThere are concerns those on a
OL,15,Frelatively low income will struggle to
OL,16,Fpay their energy bills without the
OL,17,Fsupport, with some pensioners "worried
OL,18,Fsick" about how they will heat their
OL,19,Fhomes.
