OL,3,CWinter fuel payments: What is changing
OL,4,Cand who will be affected?
OL,6,FThe government says the move is
OL,7,Fnecessary to help fill a #22 billion
OL,8,F"black hole" left by the Conservatives.
OL,10,FCommons Leader Lucy Powell said a
OL,11,Fmotion to approve the changes will be
OL,12,Fdebated on Tuesday, with the
OL,13,Fgovernment facing a possible Labour
OL,14,Fbackbench rebellion.
OL,16,FWhat is the winter fuel payment?
OL,18,FThe winter fuel payment was designed
OL,19,Fto ensure pensioners could afford to
OL,20,Fpay their energy bills during the cold
OL,21,Fwinter months.
