OL,3,CWinter fuel payments: What is changing
OL,4,Cand who will be affected?
OL,6,FIt is a one-off tax-free payment of
OL,7,Feither #200 or #300 each year,
OL,8,Fdetermined by age.
OL,10,FUntil now, it had been paid to all
OL,11,Fpensioners in England and Wales to
OL,12,Fhelp with energy bills.
OL,14,FWhat is changing and who is eligible
OL,15,Fnow?
OL,17,FThe winter fuel payment will be
OL,18,Flimited to only those over state
OL,19,Fpension age who claim pension credit
OL,20,For one of the following benefits:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
