OL,3,CWinter fuel payments: What is changing
OL,4,Cand who will be affected?
OL,6,FIf you are eligible you will be able
OL,7,Fto get either #200 or #300, depending
OL,8,Fon your circumstances, to help pay
OL,9,Fyour energy bills this winter.
OL,11,FWhile the chancellor's decision only
OL,12,Fcovers England and Wales, the Scottish
OL,13,Fgovernment also said it would end
OL,14,Fpensioners' universal entitlement to
OL,15,Fthe payment.
OL,17,FHow many people will be affected?
OL,19,FMore than ten million pensioners are
OL,20,Fexpected to miss out on the winter
OL,21,Ffuel payment this year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
