OL,3,CWinter fuel payments: What is changing
OL,4,Cand who will be affected?
OL,6,FAround 11.4 million people currently
OL,7,Fqualify for the payment, but this will
OL,8,Fbe cut to 1.5 million. The move is
OL,9,Fexpected to save the government around
OL,10,F#1.4 billion this year.
OL,12,FThere are also concerns an estimated
OL,13,F880,000 low income pensioner
OL,14,Fhouseholds are entitled to pension
OL,15,Fcredit but don't claim it.
OL,17,FPension credit is a state pension top-
OL,18,Fup, and gives you extra money to help
OL,19,Fwith your living costs if you are on a
OL,20,Flow income.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
