OL,3,CWinter fuel payments: What is changing
OL,4,Cand who will be affected?
OL,6,FThe Department for Work and Pensions
OL,7,Fsaid it had received thousands of
OL,8,Fpension credit claims since the
OL,9,Fgovernment announced it would limit
OL,10,Fthe winter fuel payment to those on
OL,11,Fthe benefit.
OL,13,FHow to check if you're eligible for
OL,14,Fthe winter fuel payment
OL,16,FIf you are eligible, you'll normally
OL,17,Fget the winter fuel payment
OL,18,Fautomatically.
