OL,3,CWinter fuel payments: What is changing
OL,4,Cand who will be affected?
OL,6,FYou will get a letter in October or
OL,7,FNovember saying how much you'll get
OL,8,Fpaid.
OL,10,FIf you do not get a letter but you
OL,11,Fthink you're eligible, you can check
OL,12,Fon the government website if you need
OL,13,Fto make a claim. You might need to
OL,14,Fclaim if you live abroad, for example.
OL,16,FWhat to do if you are not paid
OL,18,FMost payments are made in November or
OL,19,FDecember and the money is usually paid
OL,20,Finto the same account as your pension
OL,21,Fcredit or other benefits.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
