OL,3,CWinter fuel payments: What is changing
OL,4,Cand who will be affected?
OL,6,FIf you do not get a letter or the
OL,7,Fmoney has not been paid into your
OL,8,Faccount by January 29, 2025, contact
OL,9,Fthe Winter Fuel Payment Centre on the
OL,10,Fgovernment's website.
OL,12,FWhat other help is available?
OL,14,FAnyone who is concerned about whether
OL,15,Fthey can afford to pay their energy
OL,16,Fbills is urged to get in contact with
OL,17,Ftheir suppliers.
